## Privacy Policy

KiraDev is committed to protecting user privacy. Personal data collected will be used solely for the purpose of providing the best experience for users. We will not sell or share your personal data with any third parties without your consent. For more details, please refer to our privacy policy at [link to privacy policy].

## Contributions

KiraDev encourages contributions from the community. If you have any ideas or want to report issues, please open an issue or submit a pull request. We greatly value feedback and contributions from the community and will seriously consider all suggestions.

## Contribution Process

1. **Reporting Bugs**: If you find a bug, please create an issue in our GitHub repository.
2. **Submitting Changes**: If you want to change part of the code, please fork the repository and submit a pull request with a detailed description of the changes.
3. **Follow Guidelines**: When contributing, please adhere to the coding guidelines we have set. This will facilitate the integration of your changes into the main project.

## Contact

If you have any questions or feedback, please contact us via email: support@kiradev.com. We look forward to hearing from you to improve our product.

Thank you for using KiraDev's products! We hope you find value and benefit from the software we provide.
